  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">8835e348a8f14da8bf53fbd</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Whenever you give out personal information in public areas such as on a message board, chat room, comment field, or profile page, that information can be collected and used by other people. Information that you disclose in any of these forums is public information,</evidence>
